<h2>Type {{minimumLength}} random ones and zeroes</h2>
{{input type="text" value=model.contents placeholder="e.g. 0010110"}}
<p>Length: {{length}}</p>

<h2>Frequencies:</h2>
<p>The more random your digits, the more even these graphs should be.</p>
{{#each chartData in chartDataByLength}}
  {{ember-chart type="Bar" data=chartData width=200 height=200}}
{{/each}}

<h2>Your Randomness Score:</h2>
{{#if longEnough}}
  <h3>{{formatted-percent randomness}}</h3>
  <p>For comparison, I just randomly generated {{length}} ones and zeroes and got: <b>{{formatted-percent trueRandomness}}</b></p>
{{else}}
  <p>You will get your score when you type at least {{minimumLength}} numbers.</p>
{{/if}}
